<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to MotoShare</title>
    <style>
      body {
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #242424;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 600px;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        width: 500px;
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 15px 0px 15px 0px;
      }
      .header {
        border: 2px hsl(0, 0%, 13%) solid;
        background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 13%);
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 36px;
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
      }
      .title {
        margin: 5px 5px 5px 5px;
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(
          15deg,
          rgb(74 60 219) 5%, 
          rgb(255 10 108) 100%
        );
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        position: relative;
      }
      .title-decoration {
        width: 30%;
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        top: -30%;
      }
      .app-icon {
        padding: 50px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .app-icon-image {
        width: 500px;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #242424;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .content-title {
        width: 90%;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-top: 2px #4F4F4F solid;
        border-bottom: 2px #4F4F4F solid;
      }
      .content-paragraph {
        background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 16%);
        border-radius: 15px 15px 0px 0px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        padding: 15px;
      }
      .content-p1 {
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500; 
        padding: 12px;
        padding-bottom: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .content-p2 {
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 12px;
        padding-top: 0;
        margin: 0;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }
      .content-end {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 15px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      ul {
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      a {
        color: purple;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img class="title-decoration" src="{{titleDecorationUrl}}" alt="">
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to MotoShare</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="app-icon">
        <img class="app-icon-image" src="{{motorbikeImageUrl}}" alt="Motorbike">
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h3 class="content-title">Hi, I'm Jeff, I represent our team to welcome you, {{userName}} to join our motorcycle ride sharing app.</h3>
        <div class="content-paragraph">
          <p class="content-p1">If you haven't authenticated your account, please do so in the setting page.</p>
          <p class="content-p2">A quick guide to start your travel:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Select your start position and end position on built-in google map.</li>
            <li>Provide some extra information such as payment, descriptions.</li>
            <li>Select existing orders to directly start your travel.</li>
            <li>Or create your custom purchase orders to let riders know what exactly you want.</li>
            <li>Once the riders invite you, the app will send a notification to you.</li>
            <li>Then you can accept it if it meets your demand, or reject it if it doesn't.</li>
            <li>Now, you can enjoy your travel! Oh, don't forget to leave a comment once the travel is done.</li>
          </ul>
          <h5 class="content-end">
            At the end, I want to thank you again for your participation. 
            Since the app is still not on official version, if there's any problem with the app, 
            please contact me at this email: <a href="mailto:motoshare767@gmail.com">motoshare767@gmail.com</a>
          </h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <div>&copy; {{currentYear}} MotoShare Inc. All rights reserved.</div>
        <div>&copy; Partial source picture designed by <a href='https://zh.pngtree.com/freepng/ukiyo-e-waves-decoration-illustration_4763632.html'>png 圖片來源於 zh.pngtree.com/</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>